reviewText:
I'm not going to pretend to be a critic but if your a fan of exploitation / sexploitation films like myself, then do not hesitate and buy this DVD! The film is awesome, haunting music and fabulous NYC locations.
The DVD-R from Alpha video is fullscreen
 ( original ratio)
Runtime - 66mins./ 57secs
Quality is definitely watchable but not great. Also available from Sinister Cinema (DVD-R)  &  Something Weird Video ( DVD-R)
 check out both of their websites!
